cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.CY 

The paper deals with game theory and decision-making in the context of demand-side management in the smart grid. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science). The paper also proposes a novel approach based on prospect theory, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG) algorithms to solve the proposed game. Finally, the paper discusses the impact of customer behavior on demand-side management, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
